---
title: Zesty Cod Fillet with Crispy Pancetta Roasties and Garlicky Spinach
description: Pancetta and onion - a match made in culinary heaven. Throw in golden roast potatoes and garlicky spinach and you've just about hit the jackpot. Chef André, then gets you to cook cod to perfection with a delicious crispy  skin. You may just be tempted to buy a lottery ticket at the weekend after this absolute winner of a dish.
